<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- dạymaⁿạ btkẖbyny lmạ thb ạlryḥ
 bjnạḥk tdạryny wʿdk wʿd ṣryḥ
 1- lmạ ạlnạs tnsạny wạ̉sẖʿr ạ̹ny wḥyd
 ạ̉ṣrkẖ lk fy mkạny tyjy bḥb ạ̉kyd
 wtnsyny wtʿzyny yạ yswʿ
 2- lmạ ạlnạs tḥạrbny bạlạ̹ymạn ạ̉lqạk
 ṣwtk yndh ạbny ạ̉jry wạ̉bạt fy ḥmạk
 wtnsyny wtʿzyny yạ yswʿ
 3- lmạ ạlnạs bthyny wạ̉rjʿ wạ̉nạ mjrwḥ
 bṣlybk btʿyny wysẖjʿny ạlrwḥ</lyrics>
<title>dạymaⁿạ btkẖbyny</title>
